---
title: Carne Asada Beef Rump Tacos & Salsa Verde with Cos Lettuce & Sour Cream
description: Hit the streets of Mexico with a Mexican-inspired carne asada taco night. Pack these bad boys up with tender beef rump and a tomato salsa. Of course there needs to be a layer of sour cream and a salsa verde to complete the look. Taco night just got festive!
